            <h3>
            7. DISCLOSURES OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION</h3>
            <p>We will not transfer your personal data outside the European Economic Area.</p>

          <p>We may share your personal data with the parties set out below:</p>
            <ul>
             	<li>to any member of our group, which means our subsidiaries, our ultimate holding company and its subsidiaries, as defined in section 1159 of the UK Companies Act 2006 (where applicable);</li>
             	<li>external third parties such as Bullhorn (Recruitment CRM), Broadbean (Job application tool), Microsoft (Office 365) and Tawk (Live chat application); and</li>
             	<li>third parties to whom we may choose to sell, transfer or merge parts of our business or our assets. Alternatively, we may seek to acquire other businesses or merge with them. If a change happens to our business, then the new owners may use your personal data in the same way as set out in this Policy.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We may disclose your personal information to third parties:</p>
            <ul>
             	<li>where you have submitted such information in response to job vacancies displayed on our Websites, to the Employers to which the vacancy relates once you have given us permission;</li>
